graph TB
    subgraph "Feast Operator Component"
        Operator[Feast Operator<br/>Go Operator]
        HealthEndpoint[Health Endpoints<br/>8081/TCP HTTP]
        MetricsEndpoint[Metrics Endpoint<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS]

        Operator -->|exposes| HealthEndpoint
        Operator -->|exposes| MetricsEndpoint
    end

    subgraph "Feast Services (per FeatureStore CR)"
        OnlineServer[Online Feature Server<br/>Python Service<br/>6566/TCP HTTP, 6567/TCP HTTPS]
        OfflineServer[Offline Feature Server<br/>Python Service<br/>8815/TCP HTTP, 8816/TCP HTTPS]
        RegistryServer[Registry Server<br/>Python Service<br/>6570/TCP gRPC, 6572/TCP HTTP]
        UI[Feast UI<br/>Python/React<br/>8888/TCP HTTP, 8443/TCP HTTPS]
        CronJob[Materialization CronJob<br/>Kubernetes CronJob]
    end

    User[Data Scientist/ML Engineer] -->|creates| FeatureStoreCR[FeatureStore CR<br/>feast.dev/v1alpha1]
    FeatureStoreCR -->|watched by| Operator

    Operator -->|creates| OnlineServer
    Operator -->|creates| OfflineServer
    Operator -->|creates| RegistryServer
    Operator -->|creates| UI
    Operator -->|creates| CronJob
    Operator -->|creates| K8sResources[Deployments, Services<br/>ConfigMaps, RBAC<br/>PVCs, Routes]

    MLModel[ML Model/Inference] -->|GET /get-online-features| OnlineServer
    Notebook[Jupyter Notebook] -->|GET /get-historical-features| OfflineServer
    Client[Feast CLI/Client] -->|gRPC/REST| RegistryServer
    DataScientist[Data Scientist] -->|browse features| UI

    OnlineServer -->|fetches metadata| RegistryServer
    OfflineServer -->|fetches metadata| RegistryServer
    CronJob -->|materializes features| OnlineServer
    CronJob -->|reads from| OfflineServer
    CronJob -->|uses| RegistryServer

    OnlineServer -->|stores/retrieves| OnlineStore[(Online Store<br/>Redis/Cassandra/DynamoDB/SQLite)]
    OfflineServer -->|queries| OfflineStore[(Offline Store<br/>S3/GCS/Snowflake/Postgres)]
    RegistryServer -->|stores metadata| RegistryStore[(Registry Store<br/>S3/DB/File)]

    Operator -->|integrates| ODHTrustedCA[ODH Trusted CA Bundle]
    Operator -->|optional| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - Istio]
    Operator -->|optional| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth]
    Operator -->|optional| CertManager[cert-manager]

    OnlineServer -.->|optional| OIDC[OIDC Provider<br/>Authentication]
    OfflineServer -.->|optional| OIDC
    RegistryServer -.->|optional| OIDC
    UI -.->|optional| OIDC

    style Operator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style FeatureStoreCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OnlineServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style OfflineServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style RegistryServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style UI fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style CronJob fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style OnlineStore fill:#d0d0d0,stroke:#333
    style OfflineStore fill:#d0d0d0,stroke:#333
    style RegistryStore fill:#d0d0d0,stroke:#333
    style ODHTrustedCA fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ServiceMesh fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style OpenShiftOAuth fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style OIDC fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
